taken down by a mere pebble,

62
00:05:15,088 --> 00:05:17,421
if it's thrown by a master.

63
00:05:17,454 --> 00:05:20,721
The difference is in the power,
the variance in strength.

64
00:05:20,754 --> 00:05:22,288
