Itachi has shifted!

83
00:08:23,105 --> 00:08:27,072
-It seems he's finally
gotten down to business.

84
00:08:27,105 --> 00:08:31,438
So now we might get to see
the Amaterasu in action.

85
00:08:31,472 --> 00:08:32,305
-What?

86
00:08:32,338 --> 00:08:34,338
The Amaterasu?

87
00:08:34,372 --> 00:08:36,005
I can't wait to see it!

88
00:08:36,038 --> 00:08:38,472
I'm so glad we came
to see this battle.

89
00:08:41,372 --> 00:08:42,738
[clap]

