They won't slow me down at all.

145
00:12:10,630 --> 00:12:11,430
-Ah!

146
00:12:11,464 --> 00:12:13,764
We almost got caught up in that.

147
00:12:18,364 --> 00:12:19,664
ITACHI AND SASUKE: Fire Style!

148
00:12:19,697 --> 00:12:20,497
Fireball Jutsu!

149
00:12:20,530 --> 00:12:21,964
[flames blasting]

150
00:12:33,897 --> 00:12:34,364
-Mmm.

151
00:12:40,330 --> 00:12:42,297
Sasuke has the upper hand.

152
00:12:42,330 --> 00:12:43,897
I really think he's
going pull it off.

153
