absorbed Orochimaru.

223
00:19:26,992 --> 00:19:28,825
-Ah, so that's it.

224
00:19:28,858 --> 00:19:30,292
[thunder cracking]

225
00:19:33,225 --> 00:19:35,492
-Yeah, you're right.

226
00:19:35,525 --> 00:19:37,958
I don't have any
more chakra left now.

227
00:19:37,992 --> 00:19:42,725
I used up every bit of it in the
last Fire Style Jutsu attack.

228
00:19:42,758 --> 00:19:44,258
[raindrops]

229
00:19:47,225 --> 00:19:51,425
-However, do you really
believe that I would come here

230
00:19:51,458 --> 00:19:53,558
to kill you and be unprepared?

231
00:19:53,592 --> 00:19:57,392
[thunder clapping]

232
00:19:57,425 --> 00:20:00,892
-It lasts only an instant, and
this jutsu cannot be blocked,

233
00:20:00,925 --> 00:20:02,392
dodged, or evaded.

234
00:20:02,425 --> 00:20:05,992
Just like the Amaterasu.

235
00:20:06,025 --> 00:20:07,158
Now, Itachi.

236
00:20:07,192 --> 00:20:09,058
